  "title": "Applications of Quadratic Functions.",
  "body": " Applications of Quadratic Functions  You stand on a ledge 10 ft above the ground and throw a ball up in the air. The height of the ball at time seconds is feet.     At what time does the ball hit the ground?    At what time does the ball reach its maximum height?    What is the maximum height of the ball?     "
